oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Walker Lee Harvill shoeing a horse
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Walker Lee Harvill shoeing a horse named Littlelot. He is standing in front of a barn with Littlelot, an unidentified man, and an unidentified horse.
